description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you looking to expand your skills and enhance your career to include providing Complex Clinical Care or do you already have Complex Care experience?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apollo Home Healthcare is seeking experienced Healthcare Assistants to support a gentleman with complex care needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for dedicated and compassionate Healthcare Assistants who are passionate about their job, enjoy delivering one to one support and who can build positive relationships with our service users and their families.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our service user is a gentleman in his 60’s who is currently residing in Peterborough City Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We urgently require experienced Healthcare Assistants to join his care team to aid a speedy discharge back to his home in Peterborough.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We provide care to this gentleman on a 24/7 basis and supporting all aspects of his personal and social care, as well as carrying out clinical interventions as required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our ideal candidate will be committed and passionate about helping our service user return home to his family.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Experience Required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6 months previous care experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Medication Administration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Personal Care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Moving and Handling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desirable Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of Motor Neurone Disease&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tracheostomy Care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ventilation Management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oral Suctioning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gastrostomy Care (PEG Feeding)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We have the following shifts available;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Days – 12 hour shifts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nights - 12 hour shifts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why work for Apollo Home Healthcare?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We specialise in the provision of highly complex clinical care services delivered in the homes of service users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are passionate about delivering the highest standard of care and we recognise that our Nurses, Healthcare Assistants and Support Workers are integral to doing this. In return for your hard work and dedication you will receive:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible hours to suit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confirmed rotas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent rates of pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Holiday pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full clinical training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunity to work with other service users in the area&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ongoing professional training and development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We need key workers on the front line supporting our service users in the fight against the COVID-19 Pandemic. Please do not hesitate to contact our dedicated recruitment team on 01902 847111 or email onrecruitment@apollohomehealthcare.comto find out more.&lt;/p&gt;
